{"type":"article","id":16287,"title":"奇葩说邱晨被好友曝光“港独”，粉红及肖战粉开始抵制举报节目及艺人","uid":33165,"topics":[2081,978,2035,1632,2143],"contents":"杨奇函之前为邱晨好友，两人同为奇葩说辩手。<br>\n昨日杨奇函在微博公开曝光前好友邱晨的“港独倾向”，因其参与了zhan中，并发表很多“反中言论”，因此与其友尽。<br>\n于是网友开始挖坟邱晨在15年前参与占zhong并发表的相关言论，号召其他网友抵制封杀邱本人及马薇薇、周玄毅，马东等奇葩说走出的“公知恨国党”。<br>\n<b>最新更新：人民日报已经下场给定性。</b>本次举报 <b>又 “成功了”</b>。让我们恭喜厉害国广大网友和肖糊战的粉丝们。<br>\n<a href=\"https://i.imgur.com/nTG6SxV.jpg\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/nTG6SxV.jpg\" alt=\"https://i.imgur.com/nTG6SxV.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a><br>\n<br>\n<br>\n<a href=\"https://i.imgur.com/OqfMImc.jpg\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/OqfMImc.jpg\" alt=\"https://i.imgur.com/OqfMImc.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a><br>\n以下为邱晨发表的部分相关言论：<br>\n<a href=\"https://i.imgur.com/Vefs9au.jpg\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/Vefs9au.jpg\" alt=\"https://i.imgur.com/Vefs9au.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a><br>\n<a href=\"https://i.imgur.com/fBiph2G.jpg\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/fBiph2G.jpg\" alt=\"https://i.imgur.com/fBiph2G.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a><br>\n<a href=\"https://i.imgur.com/5Azyffq.jpg\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/5Azyffq.jpg\" alt=\"https://i.imgur.com/5Azyffq.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a><br>\n<br>\n由于马薇薇之前曾就肖战脑残粉事件发声，表示“粉丝行为偶像买单”。因此在一部分粉红狼和肖战粉丝的策动下，部分网民表示“<b>艺人港独公司也要负责</b>”，并开始重操“举报”大法，向文化部门举报《奇葩说》这一节目及相关“劣迹艺人”。同时有人表示：“<b>举报的人多了，即便没有问题也显得有问题了</b>”<br>\n<a href=\"https://i.imgur.com/fEFXkQ7.jpg\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/fEFXkQ7.jpg\" alt=\"https://i.imgur.com/fEFXkQ7.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a><br>\n<a href=\"https://i.imgur.com/X5hYmGR.jpg\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/X5hYmGR.jpg\" alt=\"https://i.imgur.com/X5hYmGR.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a><br>\n<a href=\"https://i.imgur.com/Jl27i6S.jpg\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/Jl27i6S.jpg\" alt=\"https://i.imgur.com/Jl27i6S.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a><br>\n<a href=\"https://i.imgur.com/7ulq9BD.jpg\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/7ulq9BD.jpg\" alt=\"https://i.imgur.com/7ulq9BD.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a><br>\n<a href=\"https://i.imgur.com/amkVNhL.jpg\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/amkVNhL.jpg\" alt=\"https://i.imgur.com/amkVNhL.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a><br>\n<a href=\"https://i.imgur.com/Wc2Zx1z.jpg\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/Wc2Zx1z.jpg\" alt=\"https://i.imgur.com/Wc2Zx1z.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a>","date":"2020-03-16","agreeCount":13,"discussionCount":0}